{"tid":1631062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論下10點鳩叫升級版","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:38.000Z","uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb15b9772d84274d8b7388959bec9a7226f9af9","tid":1631062,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"一開始10點鳩叫主要係凝聚人心，振士氣，表達民意，大家都開始叫慣叫熟，出黎行動嗌口號都冇咁怕羞，目標己達成，係時候升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 有時聽到藍絲係我地鳩叫既時候長篇大論咁鬧返我地，令我忽發奇想，不如將文宣加入鳩叫，比起連儂牆，除非你合埋耳仔如果唔係點都會聽到D。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議盡量Informative又簡短，例如&ldquo;黑警拉記者面罩，李家超講大話&rdquo; &ldquo;深水埗藍絲揸車撞到人斷腳，冷血謀殺正暴徒&rdquo;   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊口號可以照嗌，更歡迎各位每日自創新口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7d204c9a7f3f9d2f0bac1adef7b137600ee3e5","tid":1631062,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"有聲版連儂牆上線啦 1/10"},{"pid":"04cb422e89fd150666bae5defa51cd6ea2146848","tid":1631062,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"有聲版連儂牆上線啦 2/10"},{"pid":"03d838ebe70e462efd4107bb8b57ab92119dd5ba","tid":1631062,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"有聲版連儂牆上線啦 3/10"},{"pid":"fac1d96556e913f844d9933beca59c1f81ffec73","tid":1631062,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"P 牌仔唔夠力照推 4/10"},{"pid":"a8cddf90dc9b2282f57cc8bcf7938d5c388f324a","tid":1631062,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"大大力推呀 5/10"},{"pid":"73e6a978b289a937607a1c54e973713c1185fff6","tid":1631062,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"我推~6/10"},{"pid":"bcc8cf35cf346365eab4b1fe2d75c0